===Proper noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''Apache'''

# Any of several [[Athabascan]]-speaking [[people]]s of the [[American]] [[Southwest]] excluding [[Navajo]], i.e. [[Chiricahua]], [[Jicarilla]], [[Lipan]], [[Mescalero]], [[Plains Apache]], or [[Western Apache]].
# A person belonging to an Apache people.
# The languages of the Apache peoples.
# A Parisian gangster.
# An [[open source]] HTTP server.
# The town of Apache Oklahoma (zipcode 73006)

